I am writing this post for ALL Women.

“MY WHY” 🥹

I’ve had the Opportunity to Create a Company that has produced more Love + Connection than I could have ever hoped for 🙏🏻

You may recognize some of these ladies from being part of our @jennytaylorboudoirs team (Missing some 🥺)

But Last night I genuinely Realized Something….. 

I have created a company where the women Genuinely end up Becoming Friends.

Last night we met up for one of our Team Members “Celebration Dinner” and she said…. 

“Jenny, I want to say thank you for creating a company where I have been able to meet so many amazing women.”

This hit not only my heart, but my Soul.

THIS is the Treasure I realized I have been working so hard for.

I have Created a ……

GIRL GANG

FRIENDSHIP CIRCLE

CHEERLEADING TEAM

GENUINE FRIENDSHIPS

POSITIVE ENVIRONMENT

SAFE PLACE TO TELL YOUR STORIES

A COMPANY THAT HAS IS LEAD BY HEART ❤️

I Created a Space that I Genuinely Wanted and Needed in My Life 🙏🏻

My attorney recently asked me “WHY are you working so hard”…..

I said:

“I hope to have a few gorgeous homes, with killer views where I can invite all my friends to sit and watch the sunset with a glass of wine and laugh together.”

He said:

“That’s pretty simple.”

----------------------------------------

So I ask all the Business Owners this….

Are you Creating a Business for FAME, FORTUNE or FRIENDSHIP?

Be Careful, which “F” you choose above.

I choose FRIENDSHIP all day!!

At the end of life don’t “F” yourself out of what really matters…..

⬇️
My Advice…. Be really cautious of the type of business you are creating. 

If you treat your Team like Friends, guess what ….You will be surrounded by Friends.

December 28, 2023

That’s 6 months from today 

How does that feel?

It lights a 🔥 under my 🚀

It's NOT about the Lingerie❌

I did my 1st photoshoot in 2011📷

Back then I would never have been caught dead "online in lingerie" so I wore a lacy black dress out of FEAR of what everyone else would think of me.😱

12 years + 30 some Shoots Later
this is what I have learned........

I only had Judgement in myself back then.

I had a lack of confidence in who I was at the core.

If anyone wants to judge someone for what they wear on the outside, they have a LOT Of work to do on their INSIDES.

We all have flaws.  No one is Perfect.

After 5000+ clients, I know for a fact that NO ONE thinks that they look perfect. 
📺 News alert:  Perfection is an Illusion.

Every single person has something they point out that they don't love and want to change about themselves.

This is totally normal.

Our company is NOT about What is on the Outside.

I am so grateful for the thousands of women I have met throughout the years who have shared their personal stories of their life.

The good, the Bad and the UNBELIEVABLE😂 

The REASON women choose to work with @jennytaylorboudoirs is because we offer an experience that really has nothing to do with what you wear.

It's hard to explain, but let me try.....

You may think that you are booking a photo shoot, but when you walk out the door after your experience, you get something we can't really put into words.  The gorgeous photos are just the icing on the cake 🎂 
You must Try it for yourself to understand.

You choose whatever wardrobe you feel comfortable in for your photo experience ❤️

You can send our team photos from the dressing room or your bedroom mirror and we will help you decide what is going to be the most flattering in your final gallery.

Our Team will be there the whole step of the way if you need some advice.

But it always comes from someone we care about, which is why it hurts so much.

We’ve been lied to.

We’ve been cheated on.

We’ve had someone steal from us.

We’ve had friends do distasteful things.

And as life goes on, the shield that you try and build around your heart to NEVER allow yourself to feel that pain again doesn’t always work the same.

Family, Friendship, Intimate Partner, Business Associate… All Hit the Heart in different spots. 

I wish there was ONE shield you could use to NEVER allow the pain to penetrate 🛡️ 

What I’ve learned after being Betrayed multiple times…..

Release it.

Give it to God.

Life is so short.

Keep your heart soft 🙏🏻

There is a lot of GOOD in the world.

Feel the Pain for the day, but no longer.

Don’t believe that “everyone” will do this to you.

Remember YOU are the ONLY one in control of yourself.

YOU get to choose how you FEEL each and everyday no matter what external stimuli come into your realm.

Sometimes God brings Betrayal into your life to clear out space for someone more amazing to come into your life.  You just have to believe.✨

Keep your Heart open, because you never know when God will bring that New Best Friend, Colleague or Romantic Partner into your life.❤️

7 Years Ago, Life Would Change 😰

7 Years Ago Today, I signed a lease for the Very 1st @jennytaylorboudoirs Studio outside of Illinois

📍Beverly Hills, California ✨

I had stars ⭐️ in my eyes. 

We became a NATIONWIDE business 🇺🇸 

I had no idea what was in store for myself or my business 😱

I should have known, when the first client arrived and said “oh your in the Beverly Hills slums” 😂

Or when I BOUGHT our #1 competitor and Acquired her company before that BLEW UP 🤯‼️

After 10 Clients, I decided to Close the business.

I was the only investor and I lost $92,000 ❌😵

I felt like a Failure. 

I HATED Beverly Hills.

Los Angeles was NOTHING I thought it was.

Before moving there, I always thought it was the most powerful city, filled with glitz and glam, bright futures, where all your dreams come true.

LA was absolutely the furthest thing from what I imagined it was on EVER LEVEL.

I was about to Embark on the Largest Personal Developement Journey of my Life. 

California changed me, in so many ways.

7 Years Later I am Grateful to be Alive. 🙏🏻

I definitely need to release the one chapter from my future book “CALIFORNIA” 📚
